# qemu虚拟机命令行网络配置方法

## 1. 虚拟机设置
将文件拷贝到虚拟机
/usr/local/bin/setup-network-from-cmdline.sh
/etc/systemd/system/network-from-cmdline.service

systemctl daemon-reload
systemctl enable network-from-cmdline.service

## 2. host设置
添加host tap网卡设置服务
sudo cp setup-host-tap.sh /usr/local/bin/
sudo cp host-tap-network.service /etc/systemd/system/

sudo systemctl daemon-reload
sudo systemctl enable host-tap-network.service
sudo systemctl start host-tap-network.service

## 3. qemu启动虚拟机时将ip传入命令行
"IP=192.168.22.120"
